Enter to Win this Truck at 4Builds.com / @_4builds 

Wheel Specs: 22x9.5 
Tire Specs: Nitto 37x13.50/22

The HF6-2 is available in 20", 22" and 24" Diameters. 5 standard and 7 custom finishes. Starting at $649 per wheel.

VossenHF62.com
sales@vossenwheels.com
+1(305)463-7778
